_sText: Anyways, here is the V2. It contains loads of different types of textures, but it might remember you guys of some sort of a factory. It has all type of traps, from crushers, gas, lasers, electric, brakes, etc. The map trap bugs have been fixed and another secret grenade spot added. At the end you will find 2 new stages (bunny hop, knife). Here is some basic info: - Indoors - Outdoors - 3d skybox - Soundscape - 17+2 traps - 38CT spawns - 2T spawns - Afk killer > To install the map, put the new cstrike folder over your old one and over write. Hope you enjoy the map. Rating, commenting, advising is more then welcome! Enjoy! :D
